{
    "name": "Salamander",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "A warlike and tech-minded species native to the Plane of Fire, salamanders dwell in fortresses along the coasts of that plane. Other creatures, such as efreet, prize them as crafters and warriors. Mercenary salamanders find work across the planes. Mortal mages call salamanders to the Material Plane for their services. The creatures can also slip into the Material Plane where fire or heat is prevalent. A few geothermic or hothouse worlds have small salamander colonies."
        }
    ],
